      • CREATED_AT_FORMAT

        public static final org.joda.time.format.DateTimeFormatter CREATED_AT_FORMAT
        Date parser that understands the "created_at" timestamp format. The parser can cope with dates in any timezone but the returned DateTime objects will always be anchored in UTC.
